        <content><![CDATA[    <h1 class="title topictitle1">Configure CI-based remediations</h1>            <div class="body taskbody"><p class="shortdesc">Configure CI Remediations to associate workflows with CI types for manual        remediation. </p>        <ol class="ol steps" id="em_ci_remediation-normal__s_CreateCredAndTest"><li class="li step">                <span class="ph cmd"><span class="ph">Double-click the tile of the service that                            includes the CI.</span></span>            </li><li class="li step">                <span class="ph cmd"><span class="ph">On the service map, right-click the CI and                            select <span class="ph uicontrol">Remediation options</span>.</span></span>            </li><li class="li step">                <span class="ph cmd"><span class="ph">In the <span class="ph uicontrol">Remediation                                options</span> dialog box, select the remediation that you want                            to apply and click <span class="ph uicontrol">Run</span>.</span></span>            </li></ol>    </div>]]></content>
